column5: Nutanix Branded Desk Kit - Full size metal and heavy duty poly desk accessories featuring Nutanix X.
The CloudBuilders Toolkit includes: Nutanix backpack, Enterprise Cloud for Dummies Booklet, Nutanix Dress Socks, Yeti Silver Coffee Cup and a 12-piece lego block set.
16 oz stoneware: matte gray outside, glossy color inside.
